findings.title: Redeclared events
findings.description: Defining events again does not provide any benefits and hence is never recommended.

findings.title: Redundant conditional checks present
findings.description: Multiple places where specific conditions are checked multiple times, resulting in redundant conditional checks and additional gas usage.

findings.title: Unused internal __mint() function
findings.description: The LeadToken contract contains an internal _mint() function which is not used anywhere inside the smart contract and hence is unusable.
